### Correlated aggregate in subquery ###

query II
SELECT id, (SELECT SUM(val) FROM agg_test t2 WHERE t2.grp = t1.grp) FROM agg_test t1 WHERE id <= 3 ORDER BY id
----
1  30
2  30
3  30

